article_title: Man found bleeding with a cut on the neck
article_text:
Wichita police say a man is in serious condition after he was found in a parking lot bleeding from a cut on his neck.

The man was found bleeding on the ground in the 1600 block of S. Broadway near Harry after 6 p.m. Investigators say the man actually was stabbed in the 1900 block of S. Main.

It's not known what led to the man being cut. No arrests have been made.
